headline: January jobs data, Alphabet and Amazon earnings, more Warsh fallout: What to watch this week
summary: Crucial labor market data, more earnings from Big Tech giants, and continued discussion over where Kevin Warsh may lead the central bank should set the agenda in the week ahead.

headline: Assessing Whether Archer-Daniels-Midland (ADM) Looks Overvalued After Its Recent Share Price Rebound
summary: Assessing recent performance and scale Archer-Daniels-Midland (ADM) has drawn attention after a period of mixed returns, with the stock up about 14% over the past month and about 12% over the past 3 months. The company reports annual revenue of about US$83.2b and net income of roughly US$1.2b.
